    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-11-03T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-11-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="418"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d418">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 (E. W.)/11–742: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Algiers (<persName type="from"
                            >Cole</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">War Department</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="39" xml:id="d418fn39">Copy supplied by the Office of the Secretary of
                        Defense under cover of letter of September 7, 1960.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Algiers</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1942-11-03T17:00:00-05:00"
                            notBefore="1942-11-02T00:00:00-05:00">undated</date>.]<lb/>[Received
                        November 3, 1942—5 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>No. 752. [From Murphy.] Your Mike 26, 1st [<hi rend="italic">31st</hi>] Flagpole
                    and Kingpin advised. Kingpin has already sent word that in event of <hi
                        rend="smallcaps">Torch</hi> we should do everything to placate Spaniards in
                    order to avoid winter campaign in Riff thus losing time in march to Tunisia.
                    Kingpin would even favor offering territorial concession up to River Ouergha but
                    not as far as Sebaâ. [Murphy.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cole</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
